      "description": "The fun doesn’t stop on the Dutch Bros® app! Customize your drink to your liking on Order Ahead and pay with Dutch Pass®. Earn points on every purchase towards free drinks with Dutch Rewards™ and unlock exclusive app stickers! Get closer to free drinks with bonus point days and member-exclusive challenges. See you at the shop!\n\nIntroducing: \n\nOrder Ahead\nYour Broista is now on speed dial! Customize, pay and pick up your order at the shop using Order Ahead. Select \"Pickup Window\" for the fastest experience! Don’t worry, we’ll still ask about your day.\n\nDutch Rewards™\nSign up for Dutch Rewards™ and download the app to unlock a FREE medium drink! Earn 3 points for every dollar spent towards rewards. Look out for bonus point days and challenges to get closer to free drinks!\n\n*Offer valid for new app users only. Free medium drink reward upon registration. Terms apply. See dutchbros.com.\n\nDutch Pass®\nPay seamlessly with Dutch Pass®. Load funds, or add Apple Pay, and scan when you checkout to earn points automatically. You can also show luv to your Broistas by adding a tip!\n\nBirthday Rewards\nLet us treat you! Enter your birthday when you sign up & get a reward on your special day.\n\nFind Shops & Browse the Menu\nFind and favorite the shops you go to most often. Explore the menu before you order to see all of our epic flavor options!\n\nLoad Digital Gift Cards\nBuy digital gift cards & load funds to your Dutch Pass® straight from the app!\n\nCollect Stickers\nGet hooked up with digital app stickers and customize your app to show your style.",
